name: The Meta-Square | A Special Open Edition by Messhup X The Noun Square

metadata.name: The Meta-Square | A Special Open Edition by Messhup X The Noun Square 1
metadata.description:
This custom commission by amazing Nounish Artist Laureate [Messhup](https://twitter.com/messhup) depicts a futuristic Noun Square with representation of all our content & community partners, and was automatically minted by the TNS Deployer contract as a Limited Timed Open Edition, activated by the execution of Nouns DAO [Proposal 226](https://nouns.wtf/vote/226). Half the proceeds of this mint will go to TNS, half will be returned to the DAO. 

This art is for commemorative purposes only. There is no roadmap or utility, only beautiful art and a reminder that You Were Here.
